summary: A THIN SHEET OF METAL WAS PUSHED INTO THE TACK ROOM BY THE CONSUMER'S HORSE, WHICH WAS HELD TIGHT AGAINST THE BULK BY THE SEPARATION BAR AND HIS RAISING AND LOWERING HIS HEAD. WHICH CAUSED THE SHEET METAL TO PEEL AWAY FROM THE 1X1 TUBE FRAME, AND PROTRUDED OUTWARD ENOUGH  FOR THE SHOE TO CATCH AS THE HORSE LIFTED HIS LEG WHICH RESULTED THE SHARP CORNER AND EDGE CUTTING INTO THE HORSE'S LEG.    PH (LOGAN WRANGLER 2 HORSE TRAILER, MANUFACTURED BY LOGAN COACH).   *JB    *CB
